xwikidoc.title: DAV Explorer
xwikidoc.content:
{{info}} DAV Explorer does not provide a file system like abstraction to a WebDAV share. {{/info}}
[[DAV Explorer>>http://www.davexplorer.org/]] is a Java-based WebDAV client that can be used on many platforms. To test your WebDAV-enabled XWiki you must follow these steps: * Download [[DAVExplorer>>http://www.davexplorer.org/download.html]] and unpack the content. * Execute the ##DAVExplorer.jar## to bring up the client: [[image:Features.WebDAVDAVExplorer@DAVExplorer.png]]
* Enter ##http:~/~/<xwikihost>/xwiki/webdav/## in the address bar of DAV Explorer and press the [[image:Features.WebDAVDAVExplorer@ConnectButton.png]] button. * You should see something like this on the following screen: [[image:Features.WebDAVDAVExplorer@DAVExplorerRootView.png]]
* That's it! Now you can start navigating through your wiki content: [[image:Features.WebDAVDAVExplorer@DAVExplorerBrows.png]]
